Songstress, music artist and producer, SOZI, is rapidly rising to the ranks among the sea of young talent. Her debut single, b�Drinking For Two,b� electrifies with its high energy chorus and anthemic melody, followed by b�Summer Viewsb�, an exciting electropop track about the relatable urge to travel the world. A natural performer, SOZI grew up surrounded by music in a family that was always dancing, singing, and entertaining. She began classical training in piano at the age of seven and started songwriting at ten years old, a talent which she continued to cultivate as she matured and experienced the thrills and challenges of adolescent life.
